definitions.ingredient_id_missing: At least one active row missing ingredient_id.
definitions.unit_missing: At least one active row missing a recognizable unit.
definitions.unit_mismatch: At least one active row with unit not matching canonical unit.
definitions.missingVerified: Active rows have no verified forms for their ingredient_id.
definitions.mismatch: Form raw missing or does not match verified forms/aliases.
definitions.primaryReason: Primary reason is assigned by precedence: ingredient_id_missing > unit_missing > unit_mismatch > missingVerified > mismatch.
